Package jparsec.ephem.moons Description

Implements several theories of the motion of natural satellites.

This package contains algorithms designed to calculate position of natural satellites applying ESAPHO and ESADEI (Mars), E2x3, E5, and L1 (Jupiter), TASS1.7 and Dourneau (Saturn), GUST86 (Uranus), and some other theories from JPL for these and other natural satellites.
